Class NativeServerSocketImpl

java.lang.Object
  bridge.NativeServerSocketImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
NativeInterface, NativeServerSocket
public class NativeServerSocketImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements NativeServerSocket

this javase version of NativeServerSocket is essentially identical to the JavaSE version, which is in turn essentially identical to the plain java version. This implements server socket binding and an "accept" factory the key to it's success is that it also implements the raw I/O on the socket streams that the factory produces.

Author:
Ddyer
